\c 16
\nb
\v 1 Ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* laselifika kuJehu\x + 16.7,12. 2 Lan. 19.2. 20.34.\x* indodana kaHanani limelene loBahasha\x + 2 Lan. 16.7.\x* lisithi:
\v 2 Ngenxa yokuthi ngakuphakamisa ethulini, ngakwenza umphathi phezu kwabantu bami uIsrayeli\x + 14.7.\x*, kodwa uhambe ngendlela zikaJerobhowamu\x + 15.34.\x*, wenza ukuthi abantu bami uIsrayeli bone, ukungithukuthelisa ngezono zabo;
\v 3 khangela, ngizaqothula inzalo kaBahasha lenzalo yendlu yakhe\x + 14.10. 21.21. Hlab. 49.13.\x*, ngenze indlu yakho njengendlu kaJerobhowamu indodana kaNebati\x + 15.29. 16.11.\x*.
\v 4 Ofayo kaBahasha phakathi komuzi izinja zizamudla, lowakhe ofela egangeni inyoni zamazulu zizamudla\x + 14.11.\x*.
\p
\v 5 Ezinye-ke zezindaba zikaBahasha lakwenzayo lamandla akhe, kakubhalwanga yini egwalweni lwemilando yamakhosi akoIsrayeli?
\v 6 UBahasha waselala laboyise, wangcwatshelwa eTiriza\x + 14.17.\x*. UEla indodana yakhe wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe.
\p
\v 7 Njalo ngesandla sikaJehu umprofethi indodana kaHanani\x + 16.1.\x* ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* lafika limelene loBahasha njalo limelelene lendlu yakhe, langenxa yabo bonke ububi abenza emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd*, ukuyithukuthelisa ngomsebenzi wezandla zakhe, ukuba njengendlu kaJerobhowamu, langenxa yokuthi wambulala\x + 15.27,29. Hos. 1.4.\x*.
\s Ukubusa kukaEla
\p
\v 8 Ngomnyaka wamatshumi amabili lesithupha kaAsa inkosi yakoJuda uEla indodana kaBahasha waba yinkosi phezu kukaIsrayeli eTiriza, iminyaka emibili.
\v 9 Kodwa inceku yakhe uZimri\x + 2 Kho. 9.31.\x*, induna yengxenye yezinqola, yamenzela ugobe, eseTiriza enathe wadakwa endlini kaAriza, umphathi wendlu eTiriza.
\v 10 UZimri wasengena wamtshaya wambulala ngomnyaka wamatshumi amabili lesikhombisa kaAsa inkosi yakoJuda, waba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe.
\p
\v 11 Kwasekusithi esebe yinkosi ekuhlaleni kwakhe esihlalweni sakhe sobukhosi wayitshaya indlu yonke kaBahasha; kamtshiyelanga ochamela emdulini, loba izihlobo zakhe, kumbe abangane bakhe\x + 1 Sam. 25.22.\x*.
\v 12 Ngakho uZimri wayichitha indlu yonke kaBahasha, njengokwelizwi leN\nd kosi\x + 16.3.\x*\nd* eyalikhuluma imelene loBahasha ngesandla sikaJehu umprofethi\x + 16.1.\x*,
\v 13 ngenxa yazo zonke izono zikaBahasha lezono zikaEla indodana yakhe, abona ngazo, labenza ngazo uIsrayeli ukuthi one, ukuthukuthelisa iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli ngezinto zabo eziyize\x + 16.26. Dute. 32.21.\x*.
\p
\v 14 Ezinye-ke zezindaba zikaEla, lakho konke akwenzayo, kakubhalwanga yini egwalweni lwemilando yamakhosi akoIsrayeli?
\s Ukubusa kukaZimri
\p
\v 15 Ngomnyaka wamatshumi amabili lesikhombisa kaAsa inkosi yakoJuda uZimri wabusa insuku eziyisikhombisa eTiriza. Abantu babemise-ke inkamba bemelene leGibethoni eyayingeyamaFilisti\x + 15.27. Josh. 19.44.\x*.
\v 16 Abantu-ke ababemise inkamba bezwa ukuthi: UZimri wenzile ugobe futhi watshaya inkosi. Ngakho uIsrayeli wonke wabeka uOmri induna yebutho ukuba yinkosi phezu kukaIsrayeli mhlalokho enkambeni.
\v 17 U-Omri loIsrayeli wonke kanye laye basebesenyuka besuka eGibethoni, bavimbezela iTiriza.
\v 18 Kwasekusithi uZimri esebonile ukuthi umuzi usuthunjiwe, wangena esigodlweni sendlu yenkosi, watshisa indlu yenkosi phezu kwakhe ngomlilo, wafa.
\v 19 Ngenxa yezono zakhe azonayo, ngokwenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd*, ngokuhamba ngendlela kaJerobhowamu lesonweni sakhe asenzayo, ukwenza uIsrayeli ukuthi one\x + 15.34.\x*.
\p
\v 20 Ezinye-ke zezindaba zikaZimri, logobe lwakhe alwenzayo, kakubhalwanga yini egwalweni lwemilando yamakhosi akoIsrayeli\x + 2 Kho. 11.14. 2 Lan. 23.13.\x*?
\s Ukubusa kukaOmri
\p
\v 21 Khona abantu bakoIsrayeli badabukana baba zingxenye ezimbili; ingxenye yabantu yalandela uTibini indodana kaGinathi ukuze bamenze inkosi, lengxenye yalandela uOmri.
\v 22 Kodwa abantu abalandela uOmri babehlula abantu abalandela uTibini indodana kaGinathi; ngakho uTibini wafa, uOmri wasebusa.
\p
\v 23 Ngomnyaka wamatshumi amathathu lanye kaAsa inkosi yakoJuda uOmri wabusa phezu kukaIsrayeli, iminyaka elitshumi lambili; eTiriza wabusa iminyaka eyisithupha\x + 16.15,29.\x*.
\v 24 Wathenga intaba yeSamariya kuShemeri \w ngamathalenta\w** esiliva amabili, wakha entabeni, wabiza ibizo lomuzi awakhayo ngebizo likaShemeri umnikazi wentaba, \add wathi\add* yiSamariya\x + 16.28,29,32. 13.32. 20.1,10,17. 21.18. 22.10,37,38. 2 Kho. 10.1. 17.24. Ezra 4.10. Joha. 4.4. Seb. 8.1, 5.\x*.
\p
\v 25 Kodwa uOmri wenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\x + Mika 6.16.\x*\nd*, wenza okubi okwedlula bonke ababengaphambi kwakhe\x + 16.30.\x*.
\v 26 Ngoba wahamba ngayo yonke indlela kaJerobhowamu indodana kaNebati, lesonweni sakhe, enza ngaso ukuthi uIsrayeli one, ukuyithukuthelisa iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli ngezinto zabo eziyize\x + 16.13.\x*.
\p
\v 27 Ezinye-ke zezindaba zikaOmri azenzayo lamandla akhe awenzayo, kakubhalwanga yini egwalweni lwemilando yamakhosi akoIsrayeli?
\v 28 U-Omri waselala laboyise, wangcwatshelwa eSamariya. UAhabi indodana yakhe wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe.
\s Ukubusa kukaAhabi
\p
\v 29 UAhabi indodana kaOmri wasesiba yinkosi phezu kukaIsrayeli ngomnyaka wamatshumi amathathu lesificaminwembili kaAsa inkosi yakoJuda; uAhabi indodana kaOmri wabusa phezu kukaIsrayeli eSamariya iminyaka engamatshumi amabili lambili.
\v 30 UAhabi indodana kaOmri wasesenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd* okwedlula bonke ababekhona phambi kwakhe\x + 16.25,33. 21.25.\x*.
\v 31 Kwasekusithi, njengokungathi kuyinto elula ukuhamba ezonweni zikaJerobhowamu indodana kaNebati, wathatha uJezebeli indodakazi kaEthibali\x + Eks. 34.16.\x* inkosi yamaSidoni waba ngumka\add khe\x + 11.1.\x*\add*. Wasehamba wakhonza uBhali, wamkhothamela\x + 21.25,26. 2 Kho. 3.2. 10.18. 17.16.\x*.
\v 32 Wasemisela uBhali ilathi endlini kaBhali ayeyakhile eSamariya\x + 2 Kho. 10.21,26,27.\x*.
\v 33 UAhabi wasesenza isixuku\x + 18.19. 2 Kho. 13.6. 21.3. 2 Kho. 17.10. 2 Lan. 14.3. Eks. 34.13.\x*. UAhabi wenza okwengezelelweyo ukuyithukuthelisa iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli, kulawo wonke amakhosi akoIsrayeli ayengaphambi kwakhe\x + 16.30.\x*.
\p
\v 34 Ensukwini zakhe uHiyeli umBhetheli wakha iJeriko\x + 2 Kho. 2.4,19-22.\x*; wabeka isisekelo sayo ngoAbiramu izibulo lakhe, wamisa amasango ayo ngoSegubi icinathunjana lakhe, njengokwelizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* eyalikhuluma ngesandla sikaJoshuwa indodana kaNuni\x + Josh. 6.26.\x*.
